<div class="hr_aboutHR_p">
<span class="hr_aboutHR_hdr">Vision</span>: Human Resources Department aspires to deliver excellent service and innovative solutions to create a positive employment experience.
</div>
<div class="hr_aboutHR_p">
<span class="hr_aboutHR_hdr">Mission</span>: Human Resource Department supports the overall mission of AHHK of ethical leadership and excellence in healthcare services; by being a knowledgeable, approachable, professional resource in providing quality services in the areas of employee relations, benefits, recruitment and retention, compensation, and human resource information management, developing and communicating sound policies and procedures that balance the needs of employees and of the Hospital while ensuring compliance with government law, and providing strategic leadership, modeling excellence, honesty, integrity, and teamwork.
</div>
<div class="hr_aboutHR_p">
<span class="hr_aboutHR_hdr">Values</span>: Human Resources staff are committed to uphold the following values:
<ul>
<li>Be respectful and accountable</li>
<li>Be flexible and welcome different viewpoints and potential avenues of success</li>
<li>Communicate openly and honestly</li>
<li>Promote trust and integrity</li>
<li>Drive innovation to meet challenges</li> 
<li>Foster a culture of collaboration</li>
<li>Encourage growth and development to achieve excellence</li>
</ul> 
